{"type": "article", "id": 28771, "title": "云朵闹钟", "description": "", "date": "2016-06-28T06:53:22Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 44, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160703123239VPACdgZT2ULjIr6y.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>在不少作品中，梦境总和云朵联系在一起，<a href=\"http://www.muid.cc/index.html\">MUID</a> 以此为灵感设计了一款薄荷绿的云朵闹钟，希望用一种温柔的方式将你从梦中唤醒。闹钟拥有“常亮”和“节能”两种模式，使用干电池供电时会自动切换到后者，只有通过拍手或者轻晃才能激活时间显示。如果你想在床上多窝一会儿，闹铃响起后前后晃动云朵就会启动贪睡功能，五分钟后闹铃会继续响起。云朵的底部也很有特色，布满了雨滴状的凸起，看上去就好像在降下小雨一样。除了讨巧的美观上的考虑之外，这样的设计同时也起到了固定的作用。这是它的<a href=\"https://item.taobao.com/item.htm?spm=a1z10.1-c.w5003-7920026924.10.sK9PTC&amp;id=42973730616&amp;scene=taobao_shop\">购买链接</a>，售价为 89 元。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703123237t5HWkG2zUVQZMn4f.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.8384926\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703123237SBPki4dZ56HXwK9W.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67114094\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607031232382BrKe6FWRlDxO7tS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66176471\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703123238Kk0WC9qgzw7POX8o.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67516779\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}